 It premiered on [[TVN (South Korean TV channel)|tvN]] on March 23, 2020.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Shim|first1=Eon-kyung|url=http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2019/08/22/2019082201365.html|date=August 22, 2019|work=News Chosun|title=tvN \uce21 \"\uc815\ud574\uc778X\ucc44\uc218\ube48 '\ubc18\uc758 \ubc18' \ucd9c\uc5f0 \ud655\uc815..\ub0b4\ub144 \uc0c1\ubc18\uae30 \ud3b8\uc131 \uc608\uc815\" [\uacf5\uc2dd]|language=ko|accessdate=September 7, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Kim|first1=Jin-seok|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=241&aid=0002950514|date=August 22, 2019|work=Joongan Ilbo|publisher=Naver|title=[\ub2e8\ub3c5]\ucc44\uc218\ube48, \uc815\ud574\uc778\uacfc \ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 '\ubc18\uc758 \ubc18' \uc8fc\uc778\uacf5|language=ko|accessdate=September 7, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Hwang|first1=Hye-jin|url=https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=609&aid=0000159023|date=August 22, 2019|work=Newsen|publisher=Naver|title=tvN \uce21 \"\uc815\ud574\uc778X\ucc44\uc218\ube48 '\ubc18\uc758 \ubc18' \ucd9c\uc5f0 \ud655\uc815, \ub0b4\ub144 \uc0c1\ubc18\uae30 \ud3b8\uc131\"(\uacf5\uc2dd)|language=ko|accessdate=September 7, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Synopsis==\nA drama-romance between Ha Won ([[Jung Hae-in|Jung Hae-In]]) and Han Seo-woo ([[Chae Soo-bin|Chae Soo-Bin]]). Ha Won is an AI programmer and he is the founder of M&H Company. He is a consistent person with a good heart. Meanwhile, Han Seo-woo works as a classical music recording engineer. Her life is unstable without a family or house, but she is a positive person.\n\n==Cast==\n===Main===\n* [[Jung Hae-in]] as Ha Won<ref>{{cite web|last1=Yang|first1=So-young|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/star/hot-issues/view/2019/06/458006/|date=June 26, 2019|work=Maeil Business Star Today|title=\uc815\ud574\uc778 \uce21 \"'\ubc18\uc758 \ubc18' \ucd9c\uc5f0 \uae0d\uc815 \uac80\ud1a0, \ucd5c\uc885 \ud655\uc815\uc740 \uc544\ub0d0\"|language=ko|accessdate=September 7, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Choi|first1=Ji-won|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20200316000898&np=1&mp=1|date=March 16, 2020|work=[[The Korea Herald]]|title=Jung Hae-in says \u2018A Piece of Your Mind\u2019 is enough to start love|accessdate=March 19, 2020}}</ref>\n** [[Nam Da-reum]] as young Ha Won\n:An [[artificial intelligence]] programmer who founded the company M&H. He is very serious about his work though he seldom gets angry and is known as being a kind person.\n* [[Chae Soo-bin]] as Han Seo-woo<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kim|first1=Ra-ra|url=https://www.msn.com/ko-kr/entertainment/news/\ud329\ud2b8\uccb4\ud06c-\ucc44\uc218\ube48-\uce21-\u201c\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8-\ubc18\uc758-\ubc18-\uc8fc\uc778\uacf5-\ud655\uc815\u201d\u2026\uc815\ud574\uc778\uacfc-\ud638\ud761-\uae30\ub300\uac10\u2191/ar-AAG9bJS|date=August 22, 2019|work=MSN|title=[\ud329\ud2b8\uccb4\ud06c] \ucc44\uc218\ube48 \uce21 \"\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 '\ubc18\uc758 \ubc18' \uc8fc\uc778\uacf5 \ud655\uc815\"\u2026\uc815\ud574\uc778\uacfc \ud638\ud761 '\uae30\ub300\uac10\u2191 '|language=ko|accessdate=September 7, 2019}}</ref>\n:A classical [[Audio engineer|recording engineer]] who has a positive and bright personality despite her family and social issues. She likes to solve math problems when she is feeling down.\n* [[Lee Ha-na]] as Moon Soon-ho<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hwang|first1=Hye-jin|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/609/0000186311|date=October 11, 2019|work=Newsen|publisher=Naver|title=tvN \uce21 \"\uc815\ud574\uc778 \ucc44\uc218\ube48 \uc774\ud558\ub098 \uae40\uc131\uaddc '\ubc18\uc758 \ubc18' \ucd9c\uc5f0 \ud655\uc815\"(\uacf5\uc2dd)|language=ko|accessdate=October 13, 2019}}</ref>\n:A [[gardener]] and granddaughter of Moon Jung-nam, the diplomat who sponsored Ha Won. She manages her grandmother's garden and flower garden.\n* [[Kim Sung-kyu (actor, born 1986)|Kim Sung-kyu]] as Kang In-wook<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kim|first1=Jin-suk|url=http://m.isplus.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?total_id=23601463&cloc=#RedyAi|date=October 11, 2019|work=Ilgan 